      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;create-your-own-blog-from-markdown&#34;&gt;Create your own blog from Markdown!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to create a blog that seamlessly integrates with Obsidian and automatically deploys your content? In this tutorial, I&amp;rsquo;ll show you how I built my blog using Hugo, Python, and Obsidian, complete with automatic deployment and special features like Dataview table conversion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am hosting this on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.hostinger.com/cart?product=hosting%3Ahostinger_premium&amp;amp;period=48&amp;amp;referral_type=cart_link&amp;amp;REFERRALCODE=2HCANGELIPNL&amp;amp;referral_id=0194ef35-616c-70e9-afcf-90b7e3f6463b&#34;&gt;Hostinger&lt;/a&gt; to host my blog and portfolio online and I highly recommend it for the price and convenience. I utilize their Git Deployments to automatically pull the necessary files from my private repo so I can publish them on this website seamlessly and make quick edits from anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      <content>&lt;h1 id=&#34;create-your-own-blog-from-markdown&#34;&gt;Create your own blog from Markdown!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Want to create a blog that seamlessly integrates with Obsidian and automatically deploys your content? In this tutorial, I&amp;rsquo;ll show you how I built my blog using Hugo, Python, and Obsidian, complete with automatic deployment and special features like Dataview table conversion.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am hosting this on &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.hostinger.com/cart?product=hosting%3Ahostinger_premium&amp;amp;period=48&amp;amp;referral_type=cart_link&amp;amp;REFERRALCODE=2HCANGELIPNL&amp;amp;referral_id=0194ef35-616c-70e9-afcf-90b7e3f6463b&#34;&gt;Hostinger&lt;/a&gt; to host my blog and portfolio online and I highly recommend it for the price and convenience. I utilize their Git Deployments to automatically pull the necessary files from my private repo so I can publish them on this website seamlessly and make quick edits from anywhere.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;cardlink&#34;&gt;
&lt;style&gt;
